      "step_id": 0,
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "This is a simple protocol to illustrate the speaker functionality of the OT-2! With this protocol, the robot will pick up and drop a tip. Following this simple command, a song will begin to play. Using this as a template, adding a sound to your protocol should be fairly easy. This protocol allows you to select the pipette, mount, and tip rack you would like to use for this demonstration. The only labware needed will be the tip rack and this should be loaded on deck slot 1.",
